# Optional environment variables.
#
# Copy to .env.local and fill in real values, or wrap pnpm scripts with
# `op run --env-file=./.env.local --` if you store secrets in 1Password and
# want them resolved at process start.
#
# MUI X Premium components (DataGridPremium, etc.) require a license key.
# Demos work without it but render a watermark in the corner.
MUI_X_LICENSE_KEY=""
